{
  "texts": [
    "The initial density was 0.2 g cc -1 in all four cases, consistent with Chen et al.",
    "Langevin dynamics were run at a temperature of 100 K for 1 ps for relaxation.",
    "Then, the system temperature was gradually increased to 3,000 K at a 50 K ps -1 heating rate.",
    "After reaching the desired temperature of 3,000 K, the simulation was ran for an additional 10 ns.",
    "A fixed time step of 0.1 fs was utilized."
  ]
}